I currently have one of those KSC explorer contracts as I've done many times in the past, yet for some reason I can't complete this one because no matter where I go on in the area, I can't find the Astronaut Complex biome (I've even tried inching all the way around the building), so I can't do the required experiment. Currently my complex is no upgraded at all, does this have anything to do with the problem? If not, has anyone else experienced this, and how did you go about correcting it?

Thanks.
